      &lt;img alt="" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/-tix7IyA7M4RCdSDL4y0YTpw8JQ=/0x0:5326x3551/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73663613/Mavic_3_Pro_RC_Pro_lifestyle_2.0.jpg" /&gt;
